div.font:
Represents a remote control app for a smart light switch. Both the physical light switch and the remote control UI have a button that toggles the state of the switch from on to off.
The switch controller is the source of truth on the state of the switch. As such, the remote control listens for state change events and reflects them accordingly in the UI.
